<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Server Error - Luxe Time</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" />
    <style>
        .bg-dark-black { background-color: #0d1310; } 
        .bg-primary { background-color: #38a169; } 
        .text-primary { color: #38a169; }
        .bg-card-dark { background-color: #1a322c; }
        
        /* Subtle pulse animation for the icon */
        @keyframes pulse-red {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 0.8; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
        }
        .animate-error {
            animation: pulse-red 3s infinite ease-in-out;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-dark-black min-h-screen text-white flex items-center justify-center font-sans p-6">

    <div class="text-center space-y-8 max-w-2xl">
        
        <div class="relative flex justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[120px] text-red-500/20 absolute animate-error">
                history_toggle_off
            </span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-8xl text-red-500 relative mt-4">
                warning
            </span>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <h1 class="text-8xl font-black text-white/10 tracking-tighter absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -z-10 select-none">
                500
            </h1>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
                INTERNAL SERVER ERROR
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                The clock stopped unexpectedly. Our servers encountered a glitch while processing your request. Don't worry, our watchmakers have been notified.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 pt-4">
            <button onclick="window.location.reload()" 
                class="w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-primary text-black font-bold hover:bg-green-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-green-900/20">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">refresh</span>
                <span>Try Refreshing</span>
            </button>
            
            <a href="/home" 
                class="w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-300 font-bold hover:bg-neutral-800 transition">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">home</span>
                <span>Back to Home</span>
            </a>
        </div>

       

    </div>

